ly a duly trained and licensed clinical practitioner can be credentialed as CPT or PTR.	Source: The National Federation for Biblio/Poetry Therapy [7/1/2007: new]	\N	\N	\N	metaTaxonomyCode:102X00000X	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f
